NOTE:
On your pc you need to install the following with the following directories.
nsis and javahelp.  install javahelp
define the following in your ${HOME}/build.properties:
java.javahelp.jhindexer="${JAVAHELP_HOME}/bin/jhindexer.bat"
nsis.exe="${NSIS_HOME}/makensis.exe"

NOTE:
When jar file versions change (ie. colt.jar, ermineJ.jar, baseCode.jar etc.) the command line 
version of ermineJ must use these new jar files.  You can set these dependencies in the 
src/bin/forhead.conf 

WINDOWS:

(in baseCode)
cvs update
maven jar:install 
if you have made changes to baseCode, do a maven jar:deploy to update the repository on 
microarray

(in ermineJ)
cvs update
maven nsis
maven nsis-jre

// scp the above files, which will be target/ermineJ-setup.exe and target/ermineJ-setup-jre.exe onto microarray in /proj/projectpages/ermineJ/distributions

LINUX (on host where you have maven -- ie. benzer):

(in baseCode)
cvs update
maven jar:install 

(in ermineJ)
cvs update
maven jar
// To make the help jar:
maven help (This will fail if you have not generated the keystore.  See maven jnlp:generate-keystore below)

// to make generic distribution for installation
maven build-install

// to make the source distribution
maven dist:build-src

// to make the jnlp setup. Note that we are still using the help.jnlp which was hand-coded. The 1.4 jnlp plugin had to be 
// modified to include the extension element.
// maven jnlp:generate-keystore // only needs to be done once. 
maven jnlp

// DO NOT copy the ermineJ.jnlp file that is generated onto the web
server. That file has to be fixed by hand to make the ermineJ jar file
version current.


// deploy the builds to the web site (must be able to ssh to the site)

scp target/jnlp/*.jar benzer:/disk2/WWW/proj/pavlidis/projectpages/ermineJ/webstart
scp target/distributions/* benzer:/disk2/WWW/proj/pavlidis/projectpages/ermineJ/distributions

scp -r web/* benzer:/disk2/WWW/proj/projectpages/ermineJ

// to set up the distribution use build-install and then

scp target/*.tar.gz benzer:/disk2/WWW/proj/pavlidis/projectpages/ermineJ/distributions
scp target/*.zip benzer:/disk2/WWW/proj/pavlidis/projectpages/ermineJ/distributions

